reviews.text:
Chained Chinese Restaurant offers low budget options for dim sum.
 It is inexpensive especially good for family, quick bite and big groups for gathering of a meal during in early morning and tea time. However, the dim sum tends to oily in similar taste in most dishes.
Food taste was bad.. also waitress kept our change on her own will, without us telling her lol

Nice food in Hongkong business centre 
Tasty
All kinds of delicious seafood but the cheese lobster is famous, and they treat their customers right, complimentary fruits and dessert
Good tatse, excellent service

reviews.text: 海鮮新鮮👍

大廚兼老闆「三哥」坐鎮即場堂煎「蠔餅」
香味四溢
食品不錯，若100分滿分的話，值80分，地方及衛生程度都滿意。今午我和朋友坐14号枱，空調不夠，有待改善。
老闆很好，還會親自下廚做食物給客人，食材正。飯後最喜歡食佢個榴槤布丁。
老牌酒家，懷舊粵菜，吃得好，味道好..五星
